or:#667eea;text-decoration:none}@media (max-width:600px){.container{margin:0;border-radius:0}.content,.footer,.header{padding:30px 20px}.header h1{font-size:24px}.message h2{font-size:20px}.reset-section{padding:20px}}</style><div class=container><div class=header><h1>Password Reset Request</h1><p>We received a request to reset your password</div><div class=content><div class=message><h2>Hello, {first_name} {last_name}</h2><p>Someone requested a password reset for your account. If this was you, click the button below to reset your password.</div><div class=reset-section><h3>Reset Your Password</h3><p>Click the button below to create a new password for your account.</p><a href={reset_url} class=cta-button>Reset Password</a></div><div class=expiry-info><p>‚è∞ This link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons</div><div class=security-notice><h3>üîí Security Notice</h3><p>‚Ä¢ If you didn''t request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email<p>‚Ä¢ Your password won''t be changed until you click the link above<p>‚Ä¢ For security, this link can only be used once<p>‚Ä¢ If you''re having trouble, contact our support team</div><p style=margin-top:30px;color:#4a5568;text-align:center>If the button doesn''t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br><span style=word-break:break-all;color:#667eea>{reset_url}</span></div><div class=footer><p>This email was sent to {email}<p>¬© 2024-2025 {app_name}. All rights reserved.<p><a href={support_url}>Support</a></div></div>'
